Yes, it's another one of these maid cafe books by this artist. It's just as good as the other two, so I'd definitely recommend reading this one. You don't need to read the previous two to get the gist of what's happening, but you should read them anyway because they're good. I probably liked the first story the most in this one.

Happy fapping!
